		<odd type="notes">
			<head id="a6">NOTES</head>
			<p>For additional context see Community versus Commodity: Tenants and the American City
				by Stella M. Čapek and John I. Gilderbloom, 1992.</p>
			<p>Forms part of Progressive Cities and Neighborhood Planning Collections.</p>
		</odd>
